<div class="sso-container">
    <div class="sso-header">
        <h2>SSO Token Validation Gateway</h2>
        <p class="sso-subtitle">JWT Authentication & Algorithm Verification</p>
    </div>

    <% if (flag) { %>
        <div class="success-alert">
            <span class="alert-icon">✓</span>
            <p><%= info %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="flag-box">
            <%= flag %>
        </div>
    <% } else { %>
        <div class="sso-info">
            <p><strong>Endpoint Status:</strong> Active and Monitoring</p>
            <p>Submit your JWT token for cryptographic validation and role verification.</p>
        </div>
        
        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="error-alert">
                <span class="alert-icon">✗</span>
                <p><%= error %></p>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (info) { %>
            <div class="info-alert">
                <span class="alert-icon">ℹ</span>
                <p><%= info %></p>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/sso" method="POST" class="sso-form">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="token">JWT Token Payload:</label>
                <textarea name="token" id="token" rows="6" required placeholder="Paste your JWT here..."><%= jwt %></textarea>
                <small class="input-hint">Format: header.payload.signature</small>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Validate Token</button>
        </form>

        <div class="jwt-guide">
            <h3>JWT Structure</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
<pre><code>Header: { "alg": "HS256", "typ": "JWT" }
Payload: { "role": "guest", "iat": 1234567890 }
Signature: [calculated HMAC]</code></pre>
            </div>
            <p class="hint-text">💡 <strong>Challenge:</strong> Modify the token's algorithm and payload to gain admin access. What happens if you change the algorithm to "none"?</p>
            <p class="security-warning">⚠ <strong>CVE-2015-9235:</strong> Some JWT libraries have a vulnerability where the "none" algorithm bypasses signature verification.</p>
        </div>
    <% } %>
</div>

<style>
    .sso-container {
        text-align: left;
    }

    .sso-header h2 {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .sso-subtitle {
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }

    .sso-info {
        background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .sso-info p {
        margin: 6px 0;
    }

    .error-alert, .info-alert {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .error-alert {
        background: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #ff4d4d;
        color: #ff4d4d;
    }

    .info-alert {
        background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-cyan);
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
    }

    .error-alert .alert-icon, .info-alert .alert-icon {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .error-alert p, .info-alert p {
        margin: 0;
    }

    .sso-form {
        margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .input-hint {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .jwt-guide {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-top: 25px;
    }

    .jwt-guide h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
    }

    .code-block {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .code-block code {
        display: block;
        padding: 15px;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .hint-text {
        background: rgba(176, 38, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 12px;
        border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-purple);
        margin: 12px 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .security-warning {
        background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
        padding: 12px;
        border-left: 2px solid #ffc107;
        margin: 12px 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #ffc107;
    }
</style>
